The ANC pays tribute to Gavin Watson as many questions about his role in alleged state capture and the way he died remain unanswered. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Many are speculating about the circumstances surrounding Gavin Watson's death. Nelson Mandela Bay ANC Councillor Andile Lungisa says he suspects foul play. "It's part of the bigger agenda, that's why I am saying there is foul play here, you cannot because he is supposed to appear at the Zondo Commission two days, no more. We must not keep quiet we must analyse what is called a balance of forces, analyse material condition what is at play here," said Lungisa READ: Gavin Watson killed in car crash He died in a horror crash outside OR Tambo International Airport early on Monday morning.